-----

You are about to enter a world of sensual possibilities. It is a territory beyond the imaginary lines drawn in the sand, beyond the boundaries we as a species have built for ourselves. It is a place where even the most iron of wills are eroded, where the very bedrocks of human psychology are melded into a mind- and body-numbing ecstatic sensation that persists even beyond the desiccation of the physical form. Into a state of unique euphoria and unlimited pleasure. Into man's greatest lusts and deepest, darkest truths. 

One may say that paraphilias are borne of a subtle lacking, of a longing desire suppressed by the subconscious. Their persistence despite their irrationality and taboo perplex even the most experienced of psychologists. Depending on circumstance they can be a force for either pleasure or pain, but when they surface unbound, only then does **true** horror become unveiled, as lust overflows and subsumes all individuality, all memory, and all consciousness in an endless quest for perfect, unyielding euphoria. 

These tales are for those neither faint nor strong of heart.

We welcome you to the nexus of depravity. We welcome you to the Boundryless Confines.
[[/div]]

