What follows here is a burning hot reminder that the fires of our loins are not always to be trusted. For what Mr. Chive will soon come to learn is that hot dogs and hamburgers are not the only types of meat that taste better when cooked. Find it filed under "S" for "Sausage", in the fiery depths of the Boundryless Confines.

